{"data":[{"date":"09:39 02/08","title":"U23 Uzbekistan th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/u23-uzbekistan-the-hien-su-tu-tin-truoc-tran-tai-dau-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trao \u0111\u1ed5i ngay khi v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ebfn Vi\u1ec7t Nam, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n U23 Uzbekistan \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 trong l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p nhau s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</h2><h2>U23 Uzbekistan th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">G\u1ea7n n\u1eeda \u0111\u00eam ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua 1/8, \u0110T U23 Uzbekistan \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn Vi\u1ec7t Nam. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, U23 Palestine v\u00e0 Oman \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 bu\u1ed5i tr\u01b0a.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"U23 Uzbekistan th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u Vi\u1ec7t Nam  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"U23 Uzbekistan th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u Vi\u1ec7t Nam  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/u23-uzbekistan-the-hien-su-tu-tin-truoc-tran-tai-dau-viet-nam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>U23 Uzbekistan t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Trung \u00c1 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n ngay khi h\u1ecd xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u1edf s\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u00e0 ga N\u1ed9i B\u00e0i. Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng U23 Uzbekistan t\u1ef1 tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: \u201cT\u00f4i tin l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui khi \u0111\u1ebfn Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 hi v\u1ecdng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 18 v\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi Olympic Tokyo 2020. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c. Vi\u1ec7t Nam, Oman v\u00e0 Palestine \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9 \u1edf Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00e1 cao v\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u01b0a n\u1eefa. \u0110\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, \u0110T U23 Uzbekistan s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Dostonbek Khamdamov. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho CLB Anzhi \u1edf gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Nga.\u00a0<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nguy hi\u1ec3m b\u00ean ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Trung \u00c1. Trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft v\u1edbi U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u1edbi 2 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c gi\u00fap U23 Uzbekistan gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung c\u1ee7a r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 m\u1edbi nh\u01b0 V\u0103n L\u00e2m, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft, Anh \u0110\u1ee9c,..ngo\u00e0i ra nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb nh\u01b0 Quang H\u1ea3i, \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Xu\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1eddng,..c\u0169ng \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t. Do \u0111\u00f3, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng theo d\u00f5i.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-luyen-chien-thuat-moi-cho-asiad-168-192521.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/27/olympic-viet-nam-luyen-chien-thuat-moi-cho-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-luyen-chien-thuat-moi-cho-asiad-168-192521.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam luy\u1ec7n chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt m\u1edbi cho ASIAD</span><br>\r\nSau nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn ra HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111ang trang b\u1ecb th\u00eam nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edbi cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-iraq-rut-lui-mon-bong-da-nam-asiad-18-co-the-phai-boc-tham-lai-168-192516.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/18/olympic-iraq-rut-lui-mon-bong-da-nam-asiad-18-co-the-phai-boc-tham-lai.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-iraq-rut-lui-mon-bong-da-nam-asiad-18-co-the-phai-boc-tham-lai-168-192516.html\">Olympic Iraq r\u00fat lui, m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 18 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i</span><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, \u1ee6y ban Olympic Iraq \u0111\u00e3 r\u00fat \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam kh\u1ecfi ASIAD 18 sau khi \u0111\u1ed9i U16 c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y b\u1ecb t\u1ed1 c\u00e1o gian l\u1eadn tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: robotoslab-regular, serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4969","checkdouble":"192526"},{"date":"10:07 02/08","title":"\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ef1 \u00fd tr\u1ed1n \u0111i bar","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/dt-olympic-nepal-phat-5-cau-thu-vi-di-bar.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u00f3m 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ef1 \u00fd tr\u1ed1n \u0111i bar nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0110T Olympic Nepal khi h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u00ean khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y ph\u1eabn n\u1ed9.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u01b0\u1ee3t r\u00e0o \u0111i bar<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic Nepal ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 2018 nh\u1eadn tin kh\u00f4ng vui khi 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong danh s\u00e1ch t\u1eadp trung t\u1ef1 \u00fd r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i bar. Nh\u00f3m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y g\u1ed3m Bimal Gharti Magar, Bishal Rai, Hemanta Thapa Magar, Anjan Bista v\u00e0 Chirring GurungBimal.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Olympic Nepal ph\u1ea1t 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00ec \u0111i bar h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Olympic Nepal ph\u1ea1t 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00ec \u0111i bar h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/dt-olympic-nepal-phat-5-cau-thu-vi-di-bar.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110T Olympic Nepal ph\u1ea1t 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00ec \u0111i bar tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea3 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 tranh th\u1ee7 \"ph\u00e1 r\u00e0o\" l\u00fac tr\u1eddi t\u1ed1i, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed3 u\u1ed1ng c\u00f3 c\u1ed3n v\u00e0 qu\u1eady t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng trong bar \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e1ng. Camera an ninh \u0111\u00e3 ghi l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh nh\u00f3m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nepal (ANFA) t\u1ee9c t\u1ed1c v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c \u0111i\u1ec1u tra.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi ASIAD 2018<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, ANFA \u0111ang y\u00eau c\u1ea7u nh\u00f3m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean n\u1ed9p b\u1ea3n t\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 v\u1ee5 vi\u1ec7c. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, c\u1ea3 HLV Gyotuku Koji, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n Babu Kaji Basnet, l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng an ninh kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n Takkar Thapa v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 li\u00ean quan c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed9p t\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u00ecnh.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kiran Rai, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u00e1t ng\u00f4n c\u1ee7a ANFA cho bi\u1ebft: \"Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sau khi c\u00e1c c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n li\u00ean quan n\u1ed9p t\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u00ecnh\".\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nepal c\u0169ng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn d\u1eef v\u00ec h\u00e0nh vi v\u00f4 k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a nh\u00f3m 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. Trong danh s\u00e1ch tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018, HLV Koji g\u1ecdi l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i 29 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n t\u1ea1i Th\u00e1i Lan v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 3/8.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic Nepal s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Vi\u1ec7t Nam, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 Pakistan t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D ASIAD 2018.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-luyen-chien-thuat-moi-cho-asiad-168-192521.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam luy\u1ec7n chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt m\u1edbi cho ASIAD</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-iraq-rut-lui-mon-bong-da-nam-asiad-18-co-the-phai-boc-tham-lai-168-192516.html\">Olympic Iraq r\u00fat lui, m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 18 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/vtv-bi-ep-gia-ban-quyen-asiad-tha-dau-mot-lan-roi-thoi-168-192504.html\">VTV b\u1ecb \u00e9p gi\u00e1 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD: Th\u00e0 \u0111au m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n r\u1ed3i th\u00f4i!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-nhan-them-bat-loi-truoc-them-asiad-2018-168-192501.html\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u1eadn th\u00eam b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-thu-tai-asiad-2018-gui-loi-canh-bao-toi-olympic-viet-nam-168-192493.html\">\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hong-duy-noi-gi-sau-khi-mat-suat-du-asiad-168-192438.html\">H\u1ed3ng Duy n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi m\u1ea5t su\u1ea5t d\u1ef1 ASIAD?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4968","checkdouble":"192527"},{"date":"09:56 02/08","title":"\u0110T Olympic Oman quy\u1ebft t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf gi\u1ea3i T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/olympic-oman-quyet-gay-bat-ngo-o-giai-tu-hung-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u00e0 kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018, \u0110T Olympic Oman \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>Olympic Oman quy\u1ebft t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf gi\u1ea3i T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110T Olympic Oman quy\u1ebft t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf gi\u1ea3i T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110T Olympic Oman quy\u1ebft t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf gi\u1ea3i T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/olympic-oman-quyet-gay-bat-ngo-o-giai-tu-hung-2018.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Olympic Oman t\u1edbi Vi\u1ec7t Nam chi\u1ec1u 1/8</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 1/8, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Oman \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng 2018 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c tr\u00ean s\u00e2n M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 3 \u0111\u1ebfn 7/8 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau khi v\u1eeba \u0111\u1eb7t ch\u00e2n xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e2n bay N\u1ed9i B\u00e0i, \u00f4ng Said Othman Al Balushi - T\u1ed5ng th\u01b0 k\u00fd L\u0110B\u0110 Oman \u0111\u00e3 cho bi\u1ebft, sau khi k\u1ebft th\u00fac VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018, L\u0110B\u0110 Oman ch\u1ec9 th\u00e0nh l\u1eadp duy nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 v\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi c\u00e1c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau xa h\u01a1n l\u00e0 Olympic Tokyo 2020.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018, L\u0110B\u0110 Oman c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 Olympic Oman h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 7. V\u00e0 trong th\u1eddi gian qua, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn thi \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu t\u1ea1i Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n n\u00e0y, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Azani \u0111\u00e3 thu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 r\u1ea5t t\u00edch c\u1ef1c v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec3 Olympic Oman hi v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi sang Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham d\u1ef1 Gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Olympic Oman ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, tuy nhi\u00ean \u1edf c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 hai l\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y \u00c1 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00e0 0-6 v\u00e0 0-2. L\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh, th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c, Oman ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, song n\u1ebfu c\u1ee9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u23-uzbekistan-the-hien-su-tu-tin-truoc-tran-tai-dau-viet-nam-168-192526.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/u23-uzbekistan-the-hien-su-tu-tin-truoc-tran-tai-dau-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u23-uzbekistan-the-hien-su-tu-tin-truoc-tran-tai-dau-viet-nam-168-192526.html\">U23 Uzbekistan th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br />\r\nTrao \u0111\u1ed5i ngay khi v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ebfn Vi\u1ec7t Nam, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n U23 Uzbekistan \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 trong l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p nhau s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-luyen-chien-thuat-moi-cho-asiad-168-192521.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/27/olympic-viet-nam-luyen-chien-thuat-moi-cho-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-luyen-chien-thuat-moi-cho-asiad-168-192521.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam luy\u1ec7n chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt m\u1edbi cho ASIAD</span><br />\r\nSau nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn ra HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111ang trang b\u1ecb th\u00eam nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edbi cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4967","checkdouble":"192528"},{"date":"10:32 02/08","title":"\u0110\u1ec3 Son Heung-min d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018, L\u0110B\u0110 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ed9 Tottenham nh\u1eefng g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/de-son-heungmin-du-asiad-2018-ldbd-han-quoc-nhuong-bo-nhung-gi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ec3 Son Heung-min \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018, Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n r\u1ea5t c\u0103ng v\u1edbi Tottenham \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i chung.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Son Heung-min d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb World Cup 2018 khi \u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, Son Heung-min ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018. L\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 Son Heung-min d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 l\u00e0 \"tr\u1ed1n\" ngh\u0129a v\u1ee5 qu\u00e2n s\u1ef1 b\u1edfi n\u1ebfu v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, Son Heung-min v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mi\u1ec5n \u0111i l\u00ednh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u1ec3 Son Heung-min d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018, L\u0110B\u0110 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u1ec3 Son Heung-min d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018, L\u0110B\u0110 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/12/De-Son-Heung-min-du-ASIAD-2018,-LDBD-Han-Quoc-nhuong-bo-nhung-gi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Son Heung-Min ph\u1ea3i xin ph\u00e9p Tottenham m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00ean l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1eabn \u0111ang trong t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng chi\u1ebfn tranh n\u00ean m\u1ecdi c\u00f4ng d\u00e2n nam b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i tham gia ngh\u0129a v\u1ee5 qu\u00e2n s\u1ef1. C\u00e1c v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean nam n\u1ebfu gi\u00e0nh huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ea1i Olympic ho\u1eb7c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ASIAD s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mi\u1ec5n ngh\u0129a v\u1ee5 qu\u00e2n s\u1ef1.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, ASIAD 2018 kh\u00f4ng n\u1eb1m trong h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a FIFA n\u00ean CLB Tottenham c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i kh\u00f4ng cho Son Heung-min tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u. C\u00e0ng \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t h\u01a1n khi ASIAD 2018 di\u1ec5n ra \u0111\u00fang v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Premier League 2018-19 kh\u1edfi tranh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng g\u1eedi l\u1eddi xin l\u1ed7i Tottenham v\u00ec tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London c\u0169ng th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m v\u1edbi Son Heung-min khi h\u1ecd c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nguy c\u01a1 ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i ngh\u0129a v\u1ee5 qu\u00e2n s\u1ef1.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u0110B\u0110 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 Tottenham \u0111\u1ea1t ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i chung<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 Son Heung-min tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018, L\u0110B\u0110 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi Tottenham nh\u1eb1m \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t. Tottenham ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 Son Heung-min d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u hai tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p Newcastle v\u00e0 Fullham.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Son Heung Min them mot lan nua bo lo co hoi ghi ban. Anh: \u200bFIFA.\" title=\"Son Heung Min th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa b\u1edf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n. \u1ea2nh: \u200bFIFA.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/de-son-heungmin-du-asiad-2018-ldbd-han-quoc-nhuong-bo-nhung-gi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Son Heung Min d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 nh\u1eb1m tr\u00e1nh ngh\u0129a v\u1ee5 qu\u00e2n s\u1ef1.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn Fullham, Son Heung-min \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c cho \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00e0y 1/9. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1 xong v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00f9 l\u1ea1i, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp Son Heung-min trong hai tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 11/2018. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Son Heung-min c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 hai tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i VCK ASIAN Cup 2019 di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng M\u1ed9t t\u1edbi t\u1ea1i C\u00e1c ti\u1ec3u v\u01b0\u01a1ng qu\u1ed1c \u1ea2-r\u1eadp Th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t (UAE).<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111ang n\u1eb1m t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng E ASIAD 2018 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Kyrgyzstan, Malaysia, Bahrain v\u00e0 UAE.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 ASIAD 2018:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/lo-dien-cai-ten-thu-hai-se-phai-chia-tay-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-192533.html\">L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n c\u00e1i t\u00ean th\u1ee9 hai s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chia tay \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/dt-olympic-nepal-phat-5-cau-thu-vi-di-bar-292-192527.html\">\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ef1 \u00fd tr\u1ed1n \u0111i bar</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-luyen-chien-thuat-moi-cho-asiad-168-192521.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam luy\u1ec7n chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt m\u1edbi cho ASIAD</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-iraq-rut-lui-mon-bong-da-nam-asiad-18-co-the-phai-boc-tham-lai-168-192516.html\">Olympic Iraq r\u00fat lui, m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 18 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/vtv-bi-ep-gia-ban-quyen-asiad-tha-dau-mot-lan-roi-thoi-168-192504.html\">VTV b\u1ecb \u00e9p gi\u00e1 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD: Th\u00e0 \u0111au m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n r\u1ed3i th\u00f4i!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-nhan-them-bat-loi-truoc-them-asiad-2018-168-192501.html\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u1eadn th\u00eam b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4966","checkdouble":"192532"},{"date":"10:20 02/08","title":"L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n c\u00e1i t\u00ean th\u1ee9 hai s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chia tay \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/1/lo-dien-cai-ten-thu-hai-se-phai-chia-tay-dt-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp chi\u1ec1u 1/8 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 2 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay ASIAD.</h2><h2>Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1ebb PVF t\u1ea1i H\u01b0ng Y\u00ean, chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua 1/8, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi m\u1eb7t s\u00e2n M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho gi\u1ea3i U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 3 \u0111\u1ebfn 7/8.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n c\u00e1i t\u00ean th\u1ee9 hai s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chia tay \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n c\u00e1i t\u00ean th\u1ee9 hai s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chia tay \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/Lo-dien-cai-ten-thu-hai-se-phai-chia-tay-DT-Olympic-Viet-Nam-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u00e1i t\u00ean ti\u1ebfp theo\u00a0chia tay \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp n\u00e0y, HLV Park Hang Seo ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 trong tay 28 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u00e0nh l\u1eb7n, bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Tr\u1ecdng \u0110\u1ea1i sau m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i b\u1edfi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u1eadt c\u1ed5 ch\u00e2n. Trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua, Tr\u1ecdng \u0110\u1ea1i cho th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 m\u00ecnh \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t khi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n tr\u01a1n tru b\u00e0i kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ea7u bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lo ng\u1ea1i l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 Nguy\u1ec5n Phong H\u1ed3ng Duy v\u00e0 Ph\u1ea1m Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh \u0111ang g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 v\u1eabn \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp ri\u00eang v\u1edbi gi\u00e1o \u00e1n ri\u00eang c\u1ee7a b\u00e1c s\u1ef9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c Choi Joo Yong, ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eebng \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb cho danh th\u1ee7 Park Ji Sung, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 HAGL Tu\u1ea5n Anh.. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong 2 c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00e0y, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n Phong H\u1ed3ng Duy \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chia tay Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1edfi g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u00e1ch c\u01a1. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a HAGL \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho ph\u00e9p ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 y t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh\u00a0\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng tuy nhi\u00ean l\u00fac n\u00e0y anh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ch\u1ed1t danh s\u00e1ch 20 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 7/8 t\u1edbi, n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 anh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean ti\u1ebfp theo sau H\u1ed3ng Duy ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay ASIAD 2018. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf cho \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1edfi ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ngh\u1ec7 An \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 kh\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, nhanh nh\u1eb9n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u00f3ng v\u1ea5n b\u00e1o ch\u00ed m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u00f4ng Park th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 lo l\u1eafng n\u1ebfu c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 th\u00eam ca ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00e0o n\u1eefa sau gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf tr\u00ean s\u00e2n M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh. Theo k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ch\u1ed1t qu\u00e2n s\u1ed1 v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 7/8 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Indonesia v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 11 t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-oman-quyet-gay-bat-ngo-o-giai-tu-hung-2018-168-192528.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/olympic-oman-quyet-gay-bat-ngo-o-giai-tu-hung-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-oman-quyet-gay-bat-ngo-o-giai-tu-hung-2018-168-192528.html\">\u0110T Olympic Oman quy\u1ebft t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf gi\u1ea3i T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng 2018</span><br>\r\nL\u00e0 kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018, \u0110T Olympic Oman \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/dt-olympic-nepal-phat-5-cau-thu-vi-di-bar-292-192527.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/dt-olympic-nepal-phat-5-cau-thu-vi-di-bar.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/dt-olympic-nepal-phat-5-cau-thu-vi-di-bar-292-192527.html\">\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ef1 \u00fd tr\u1ed1n \u0111i bar</span><br>\r\nNh\u00f3m 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ef1 \u00fd tr\u1ed1n \u0111i bar nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0110T Olympic Nepal khi h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u00ean khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y ph\u1eabn n\u1ed9.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u23-uzbekistan-the-hien-su-tu-tin-truoc-tran-tai-dau-viet-nam-168-192526.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/u23-uzbekistan-the-hien-su-tu-tin-truoc-tran-tai-dau-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u23-uzbekistan-the-hien-su-tu-tin-truoc-tran-tai-dau-viet-nam-168-192526.html\">U23 Uzbekistan th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nTrao \u0111\u1ed5i ngay khi v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ebfn Vi\u1ec7t Nam, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n U23 Uzbekistan \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 trong l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p nhau s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: robotoslab-regular, serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4965","checkdouble":"192533"},{"date":"10:34 02/08","title":"Tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Paris Saint Germain: Neymar, Justin Timberlake v\u00e0 Jumpman","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/psg-2.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eb1m tho\u00e1t ly ra kh\u1ecfi b\u1ea7u s\u1eefa m\u1eb9 t\u1eeb Qatar, Paris Saint Germain \u0111ang \u0111i nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u00e0 r\u1ea5t \u00edt c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 ch\u00fa t\u00e2m khai ph\u00e1 - l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ecba th\u1eddi trang.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u00f2n non tr\u1ebb n\u1ebfu so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u00f4ng l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u (th\u00e0nh l\u1eadp n\u0103m 1970), Paris Saint Germain ch\u1ec9 d\u1ea7n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a l\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ecba gi\u00e0 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2011. D\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 b\u1edfi Qatar Sports Investments bi\u1ebfn PSG tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ebf l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p, v\u01b0\u01a1n m\u00ecnh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u00f4ng l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u th\u1eddi hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Paris Saint Germain Neymar, Justin Timberlake, h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Paris Saint Germain Neymar, Justin Timberlake, h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/psg.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Paris Saint Germain l\u00e0 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u kinh doanh \u0111\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1eafm \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0 nh\u00f3m c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nK\u1ec3 t\u1eeb c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c n\u0103m 2011, PSG v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ligue 1 \u0111\u1ebfn 5 l\u1ea7n ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3y n\u0103m. Trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i b\u1ed1n th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, PSG m\u1edbi hai l\u1ea7n n\u00e2ng c\u00fap v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd c\u1ee7a d\u00f2ng ti\u1ec1n &quot;\u0111\u1ea7y m\u00f9i d\u1ea7u&quot; t\u1eeb Qatar \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng c\u00e0ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o PSG c\u00e0ng lo l\u1eafng. Nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb d\u00f2ng ti\u1ec1n ch\u1ea3y v\u00e0o t\u1eeb Qatar. Th\u1eed t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 n\u1ebfu Qatar c\u1eaft \u0111\u1ee9t hay gi\u1ea3m ngu\u1ed3n t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3, PSG s\u1ebd ra sao?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Les Parisiens&quot; bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch &quot;t\u1ef1 l\u1eadp&quot; nh\u01b0 ph\u1ea7n \u0111a nh\u1eefng \u00f4ng l\u1edbn truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111ang l\u00e0m b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch th\u00e2m nh\u1eadp v\u00e0o th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng.</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed9c b\u1eaft tay v\u1edbi &quot;Jumpman&quot;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Jumpman&quot; l\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 b\u00f3ng r\u1ed5 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n b\u1edfi Nike, v\u1edbi ngu\u1ed3n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb c\u00fa &quot;slam dunk&quot; c\u1ee7a huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng r\u1ed5 Michael Jordan. Th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0y ban \u0111\u1ea7u ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n gi\u00e0y b\u00f3ng r\u1ed5, sau \u0111\u00f3 ti\u1ebfn xa h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ebfn l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c th\u1eddi trang th\u1ec3 thao.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"PSG bat tay voi Jumpman de lan san sang linh vuc thoi trang.\" title=\"PSG b\u1eaft tay v\u1edbi Jumpman \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5n s\u00e2n sang l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c th\u1eddi trang.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/psg-1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>PSG b\u1eaft tay v\u1edbi Jumpman \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5n s\u00e2n sang l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c th\u1eddi trang.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00fa b\u1eaft tay l\u1ecbch s\u1eed gi\u1eefa PSG v\u1edbi Jumpman th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i tham v\u1ecdng, c\u0169ng gi\u00e0u toan t\u00ednh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p. Thay v\u00ec c\u1ed1 chen ch\u00e2n v\u00e0o th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng vi\u1ec5n \u0111\u00f4ng v\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh mi\u1ebfng b\u00e1nh ngon l\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng \u00f4ng l\u1edbn truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 Real Madrid, Manchester United hay Barcelona, PSG h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng b\u1ea3n s\u1eafc ri\u00eang cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u CLB.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1eb1m \u1edf m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng kinh \u0111\u00f4 th\u1eddi trang th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi (Paris), PSG h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ecb ph\u1ea7n d\u00e0nh cho t\u00edn \u0111\u1ed3 th\u1eddi trang. PSG b\u1eaft tay v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao ca nh\u1ea1c \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u00edt \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng khai th\u00e1c, \u00edt c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u00e0 gi\u00e0u ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng h\u01a1n.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng t\u00edn \u0111\u1ed3 y\u00eau \u00e2m nh\u1ea1c, y\u00eau th\u1eddi trang, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd t\u00ecm \u0111\u1ebfn PSG th\u00f4ng qua hai ph\u01b0\u01a1ng di\u1ec7n n\u00e0y, thay v\u00ec ph\u01b0\u01a1ng di\u1ec7n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u01a1n thu\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ao dau mua giai 2018-19 duoc thiet ke voi cam hung tu song am nhac.\" title=\"\u00c1o \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf v\u1edbi c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng t\u1eeb s\u00f3ng \u00e2m nh\u1ea1c.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/psg-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u00c1o \u0111\u1ea5u PSG m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf v\u1edbi c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng t\u1eeb s\u00f3ng \u00e2m nh\u1ea1c.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPSG s\u1ebd b\u1eaft tay v\u1edbi &quot;Jumpman&quot; ph\u00e1t h\u00e0nh d\u00f2ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m th\u1eddi trang v\u1edbi nh\u00e3n hi\u1ec7u pha tr\u1ed9n gi\u1eefa c\u1ea3 hai. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh &quot;Jumpman&quot; bay ng\u01b0\u1eddi&nbsp; v\u01b0\u01a1n t\u1edbi th\u00e1p Eiffel. Trong s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n \u00e2m nh\u1ea1c g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Paris, nam ca s\u0129 Justin Timberlake \u0111\u00e3 m\u1eb7c chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o jacket c\u00f3 logo c\u1ee7a nh\u00e3n hi\u1ec7u th\u1eddi trang k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa PSG v\u00e0 &quot;Jumpman&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0ng trong n\u0103m nay. PSG \u0111ang \u0111i m\u1ed9t con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1edbi m\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u01b0a c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 n\u00e0o l\u00e0m, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u tr\u00ean l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p th\u1eddi trang, t\u1eeb th\u1eddi trang thu h\u00fat th\u00eam ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1.</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">X\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng ph\u00f4ng v\u0103n h\u00f3a</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u01a1n m\u00ecnh tr\u00ean l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u, PSG \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng m\u1ed9t ph\u00f4ng v\u0103n h\u00f3a ri\u00eang, k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa th\u1eddi trang, gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed v\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, DJ Snake g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong \u0111o\u1ea1n phim ng\u1eafn gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u cho tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 v\u00f2ng 1/8 Champions League g\u1eb7p Real Madrid t\u1ea1i Parc des Princes.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"PSG hop tac voi nhung ngoi sao ca nhac noi tieng de quang ba cho thuong hieu thoi trang.\" title=\"PSG h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao ca nh\u1ea1c n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u1ec3 qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u th\u1eddi trang.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/beyonce.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>PSG h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao ca nh\u1ea1c n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng nh\u01b0 Beyonce \u0111\u1ec3 qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u th\u1eddi trang.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 nh\u1eb1m pha tr\u1ed9n gi\u1eefa th\u1ec3 thao v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed, bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 vi\u1ec7c b\u1eaft tay v\u1edbi Timberlake. Ti\u1ebfp theo \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd m\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Beyonce qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u nh\u1eb1m h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi ph\u00e1i n\u1eef, th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng m\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u01b0a khai th\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">PSG h\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh s\u1ef1 h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. V\u00ec v\u1eady, h\u1ecd b\u1eaft tay v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ca s\u0129 ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu \u1edf hai d\u00f2ng nh\u1ea1c pop v\u00e0 hip-hop v\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u1ea7n \u0111a ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u1ebb \u01b0a chu\u1ed9ng.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Xu h\u01b0\u1edbng n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n qua vi\u1ec7c Drake qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 cho \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u \u0110T Mexico, hay 2 Chainz qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 cho \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Atlanta United. V\u00e0 PSG \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ea1i l\u00e0 s\u1ebd b\u1eaft tay v\u1edbi Kanye West \u0111\u1ec3 qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nhung thuong vu dat gia nhu Neymar va Mbappe the hien tham vong cua Paris Saint Germain.\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u01b0 Neymar v\u00e0 Mbappe th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Paris Saint Germain.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/neymar-mbappe.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u01b0 Neymar v\u00e0 Mbappe th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Paris Saint Germain.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c b\u1eaft tay v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao ca nh\u1ea1c, PSG c\u0169ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111i theo b\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 khu\u1ebfch tr\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh. X\u00e9t cho c\u00f9ng, c\u1ed1t l\u00f5i \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1n x\u00e9t th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 v\u1eabn l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u, s\u1ef1 thu h\u00fat v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u PSG hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang thi\u1ebfu. V\u00ec v\u1eady, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebfc ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 mang t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n cho t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai nh\u01b0 Kylian Mbappe hay \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Neymar. Tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a PSG c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh cao Champions League \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u, qua \u0111\u00f3 thu h\u00fat nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n h\u01a1n t\u1eeb b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n, t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3, b\u00e1n s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m,...<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">X\u00e9t cho c\u00f9ng, PSG mu\u1ed1n tho\u00e1t ly ra kh\u1ecfi b\u1ea7u s\u1eefa m\u1eb9 t\u1eeb Qatar \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng tr\u00ean \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00e2n ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh nh\u01b0 nhi\u1ec1u \u00f4ng l\u1edbn kh\u00e1c t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111ang l\u00e0m. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Nh\u01b0 \u0110\u1ea1t (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4964","checkdouble":"192336"},{"date":"09:34 02/08","title":"Jose Mourinho: \"Ronaldo l\u00e0m sao l\u1edbn h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i Real Madrid \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/15/jose-mourinho-nhan-xet-ve-real-madrid-va-ronaldo.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong h\u00e8 2018, Jose Mourinho cho r\u1eb1ng Cristiano Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u00e0o l\u1edbn h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 Real Madrid \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018, Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua Man Utd v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 1-2. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Los Blancos b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u ra s\u00e2n m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo, ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jose Mourinho nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 Real Madrid v\u00e0 Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jose Mourinho nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 Real Madrid v\u00e0 Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/Jose-Mourinho-nhan-xet-ve-Real-Madrid-va-Ronaldo-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Jose Mourinho nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 Real Madrid sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i ICC 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKarim Benzema l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t cho Real Madrid. Ngo\u00e0i ra, h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Los Blancos c\u00f2n c\u00f3 Gareth Bale v\u00e0 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Vinicius Junior. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Real Madrid \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha loan tin v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Eden Hazard (Chelsea).<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mourinho nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 Real Madrid<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eebng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Real Madrid, Jose Mourinho nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t r\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Ronaldo th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn Los Blancos: \"M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft Ronaldo nh\u01b0ng m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft Real Madrid ra sao. T\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd nh\u1edb m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 Cristiano Ronaldo nh\u01b0ng Real Madrid t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean l\u1edbn h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o\".\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 Real Madrid th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1, c\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 Man Utd v\u1eady. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, l\u00e0 t\u1eadp h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c nhau. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ed9t, s\u1ed1 kh\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u01b0\u1ee3n, s\u1ed1 kh\u00e1c t\u1eeb Castilla, s\u1ed1 kh\u00e1c t\u1eeb c\u1ea3 Real Madrid C\".\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Real Madrid th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u, h\u1ecd c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb b\u1edfi La Liga kh\u1edfi tranh mu\u1ed9n h\u01a1n Premier League\".</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Real Madrid h\u00e8 2018:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/mourinho-muon-mu-chieu-mo-bo-doi-cua-real-187-192515.html\">Mourinho mu\u1ed1n M.U chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i c\u1ee7a Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-28-sao-that-sung-cua-real-khuoc-tu-mu-184-192511.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 2/8: Sao th\u1ea5t s\u1ee7ng c\u1ee7a Real kh\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/kovacic-khong-den-mu-vi-mourinho-184-192497.html\">Sao Real t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i MU v\u00ec Mourinho</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-lopetegui-phat-bieu-ve-viec-real-mua-courtois-180-192483.html\">HLV Lopetegui n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n Real mu\u1ed1n mua Courtois?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-mu-hlv-mourinho-dang-rat-hanh-phuc-172-192473.html\">Sao M.U: HLV Mourinho \u0111ang r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/odriozola-phat-bieu-sau-tran-mu-21-real-180-192470.html\">T\u00e2n binh 40 tri\u1ec7u Euro c\u1ee7a Real n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn ra m\u1eaft?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4963","checkdouble":"192522"},{"date":"10:38 02/08","title":"Nh\u1edd John Terry, Chelsea s\u1eafp c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/nho-john-terry-chelsea-sap-co-jack-grealish.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Jack Grealish c\u1ee7a Aston Villa, nh\u1edd huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i John Terry \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London s\u1eafp s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m Jack Grealish</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Jack Grealish l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Aston Villa. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1995 l\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111a n\u0103ng, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m, h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng, ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ho\u1eb7c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1eafm.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Jack Grealish v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Jack Grealish v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/Chelsea-muon-co-Jack-Grealish-voi-gia-20-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jack Grealish \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i ghi 3 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 6 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng, v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Aston Villa l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/liverpool-van-muon-mua-grealish-172-190672.html\" target=\"_blank\">Liverpool mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Jack Grealish</span>, Tottenham v\u00e0 M.U c\u0169ng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995. Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n Jack Grealish \u0111ang b\u1ecb dao \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Aston Villa \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Villa Park \u0111\u00f2i 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, song v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00f2i ra \u0111i, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 Aston Villa s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thu v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n nh\u01b0 mong mu\u1ed1n.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi m\u00e0 TTCN \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u0111ang \u0111i v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Aston Villa.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea s\u1eafp s\u1edf h\u1eefu Jack Grealish</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Jack Grealish c\u1ee7a Aston Villa, nh\u1edd huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i John Terry \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London s\u1eafp s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea sap co Jack Grealish\" title=\"Chelsea s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Jack Grealish\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/nho-john-terry-chelsea-sap-co-jack-grealish.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Jack Grealish</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nThe Blues m\u1edbi gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995, nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i \u0111ang chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf v\u00ec ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n. Theo \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea c\u0169ng c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf h\u01a1n nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp b\u1edfi huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i John Terry \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Aston Villa nh\u1ea3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i cho The Blues.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Terry \u0111\u00e1 cho Villa theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, anh l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Villa Park. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1980 \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Villa b\u00e1n Grealish cho Chelsea v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea m\u1edbi c\u00f3 2 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, HLV Sarri \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi. N\u1ebfu The Blues th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m v\u1ee5 Grealish, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4962","checkdouble":"192529"},{"date":"10:54 02/08","title":"Sao tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u1ec9 ra v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 Chelsea c\u1ea7n kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/sao-tuyen-duc-chi-ra-van-de-chelsea-can-khac-phuc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ec3 thua Arsenal trong tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, trung v\u1ec7 Rudiger ch\u1ec9 ra v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a Chelsea t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nRudiger mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i Dublin, The Blues \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1, d\u00f9 h\u1ecd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc do c\u00f4ng trung v\u1ec7 Antonio Rudiger. Nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 l\u01a1i l\u1ecfng trong h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Alvaro Morata b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn Chelsea ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1, khi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0, ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edf \u0111i\u1ec3m Rudiger cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 trong n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng s\u1edbm, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng l\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i n\u1edbi r\u1ed9ng c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t trong hi\u1ec7p 1. V\u00e0o nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p, to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 c\u1ea9u th\u1ea3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rudiger ch\u1ec9 ra v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a Chelsea trong tr\u1eadn thua Arsenal\" title=\"Rudiger ch\u1ec9 ra v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/sao-tuyen-duc-chi-ra-van-de-chelsea-can-khac-phuc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Rudiger ch\u1ec9 ra v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a Chelsea trong tr\u1eadn thua Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng quy\u1ec1n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn cho Arsenal, v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c nh\u01b0 v\u1eady trong hi\u1ec7p 2. Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00fang t\u00f4i tung ra, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u Chelsea c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n nhanh ch\u00f3ng. Trong hi\u1ec7p 2, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra c\u1edfi m\u1edf h\u01a1n, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua khi \u0111\u00e1ng ra ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3&rdquo; &ndash; Antonio Rudiger cho bi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1eeb t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c, trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui khi gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n. \u0110\u00f3 lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd ghi th\u1eadt nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Rudiger ch\u1ec9 ra v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a Chelsea, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u1ea7n nhanh ch\u00f3ng kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, The Blues s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Man City \u0111\u1ec3 tranh Community Shield. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c g\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i Arsenal t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 2 c\u1ee7a Premier League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hoc-martial-sao-chelsea-lan-mat-tam-khien-hlv-sarri-to-ra-kho-chiu-172-192525.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/23/hoc-martial-sao-chelsea-lan-mat-tam-khien-hlv-sarri-to-ra-kho-chiu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hoc-martial-sao-chelsea-lan-mat-tam-khien-hlv-sarri-to-ra-kho-chiu-172-192525.html\">H\u1ecdc Martial, sao Chelsea l\u1eb7n m\u1ea5t t\u0103m khi\u1ebfn HLV Sarri t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00e2n thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Chelsea &ndash; HLV Sarri ph\u00e0n n\u00e0n v\u1ec1 Willian khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y m\u1ea5t t\u00edch v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-chelsea-muon-da-tan-cong-phai-cho-kante-172-192492.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/goc-chelsea-muon-da-tan-cong-phai-cho-kante.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-chelsea-muon-da-tan-cong-phai-cho-kante-172-192492.html\">G\u00f3c Chelsea: Mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng? Ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd Kante</span><br>\r\nCh\u00fang ta v\u1eabn quen v\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh ng\u00f4i sao tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p c\u00e0y n\u00e1t khu trung tuy\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, nh\u01b0ng Kante t\u1ea1i Chelsea m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i sau s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-arsenal-11-pen-65-chelsea-icc-2018-326-192505.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/video-tong-hop-arsenal-11-pen-65-chelsea-icc-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-arsenal-11-pen-65-chelsea-icc-2018-326-192505.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Arsenal 1-1 (pen 6-5) Chelsea (ICC 2018)</span><br>\r\n\u00cdt nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n \u1edf tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu t\u1ea1i ICC 2018 song Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb d\u1eabn b\u00e0n t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edbi ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4961","checkdouble":"192530"},{"date":"10:58 02/08","title":"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Arsenal mu\u1ed1n Klopp k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/20/huyen-thoai-arsenal-muon-klopp-ky-hop-dong-voi-nha-vo-dich-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Robert Pires ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Arsenal mu\u1ed1n HLV Klopp \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Nabil Fekir c\u1ee7a Lyon trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 CN H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nabil Fekir t\u1eebng l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Liverpool</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Nabil Fekir l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t Ligue 1 v\u00e0 l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Lyon. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1993 ghi 18 b\u00e0n \u1edf Ligue 1 v\u00e0 24 b\u00e0n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Robert Pires ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool v\u1ee5 Nabil Fekir h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Robert Pires ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool v\u1ee5 Nabil Fekir h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/29/Robert-Pires-phat-bieu-ve-Liverpool-vu-Nabil-Fekir-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool t\u1eebng r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Fekir</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Liverpool. HLV Klopp \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, \u00f4ng th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp g\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec7n thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1993 t\u1edbi Anfield.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Lyon nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Liverpool ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 60 tri\u1ec7u euro. Khi qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i th\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u1ed5i \u00fd, kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh n\u1eefa.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nThe Kop sau \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Xherdan Shaqiri t\u1eeb Stoke City. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9, L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p n\u1eefa. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/liverpool-chanh-noi-khong-voi-nha-vo-dich-world-cup-172-191696.html\" target=\"_blank\">Liverpool t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i mua Fekir </span>khi b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Lyon m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Robert Pires v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n Liverpool mua Nabil Fekir</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Robert Pires ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Arsenal mu\u1ed1n HLV Klopp \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Nabil Fekir c\u1ee7a Lyon trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 CN H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Robert Pires ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool v\u1ee5 Nabil Fekir h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Robert Pires ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool v\u1ee5 Nabil Fekir h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/25/Robert-Pires-phat-bieu-ve-Liverpool-vu-Nabil-Fekir-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Robert Pires v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n Liverpool mua\u00a0</span>Nabil Fekir</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cFekir l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o cho Liverrpool, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft t\u1ea1i sao qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n l\u1ea1i b\u1ecb tr\u00ec ho\u00e3n, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Liverpool\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Klopp x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc n\u1ebfu Liverpool b\u1ecf qua c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. C\u00f3 Nabil Fekir, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Klopp s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Klopp tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng mua th\u00eam c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf ra 175 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Fabinho, Naby Keita, Alisson v\u00e0 Xherdan Shaqiri.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4960","checkdouble":"192531"},{"date":"11:07 02/08","title":"D\u00f9ng doping, sao kh\u1ee7ng Premier League nh\u1eadn \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2... 18 th\u00e1ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/dung-doping-sao-khung-premier-league-nhan-an-treo-gio-18-thang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Arsenal v\u00e0 Man City \u2013 Samir Nasri b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 18 th\u00e1ng v\u00ec s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ch\u1ea5t c\u1ea5m.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nNasri b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 2 v\u1eeba qua, Nasri \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2 6 th\u00e1ng v\u00ec s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng doping. Tuy nhi\u00ean theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, UEFA c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t n\u00e0y ch\u01b0a h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, v\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e2ng m\u1ee9c ph\u1ea1t l\u00ean t\u1edbi 18 th\u00e1ng cho c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Man City.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p trong th\u1eddi gian kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Sevilla d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1m t\u1ea1i Los Angeles v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 12/2016 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. T\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u00eam m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5t c\u00f3 trong m\u1ee5c c\u1ea5m s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe, v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng may \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb C\u01a1 quan ph\u00f2ng ch\u1ed1ng doping tu\u00fdt c\u00f2i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nasri b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 18 th\u00e1ng v\u00ec s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng doping \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb\" title=\"Nasri b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 18 th\u00e1ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/dung-doping-sao-khung-premier-league-nhan-an-treo-gio-18-thang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nasri b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 18 th\u00e1ng v\u00ec s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng doping \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Sevilla gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i, v\u00e0 c\u0169ng b\u1ecb Man City s\u1edbm thanh l\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. T\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 8/2017, anh gia nh\u1eadp CLB Antalyaspor \u1edf Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 8 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m nay. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u00f3n h\u00e0ng t\u1ef1 do tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi nh\u1eadn m\u1ee9c \u00e1n m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t 18 th\u00e1ng treo gi\u00f2.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a UEFA, m\u1ee9c \u00e1n n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t may l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 7/2017. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a Nasri s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 11 n\u0103m nay. Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o d\u00f9 phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3, b\u1edfi Nasri l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ef1 do.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng tin r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng bu\u1ed3n cho c\u1ef1u sao Arsenal, ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eebng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 \u1edf Premier League, v\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin trong th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i La Liga. Vi\u1ec7c&nbsp;Samir Nasri b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 18 th\u00e1ng v\u00ec s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng doping s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec9nh cao, b\u1edfi n\u0103m nay anh \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 31.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/tuyen-thu-phap-khoe-sieu-xe-ferrari-khi-tro-lai-hoi-quan-cung-man-city-188-192477.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/tuyen-thu-phap-khoe-sieu-xe-ferrari-khi-tro-lai-hoi-quan-cung-man-city.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/hau-truong/tuyen-thu-phap-khoe-sieu-xe-ferrari-khi-tro-lai-hoi-quan-cung-man-city-188-192477.html\">Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p khoe si\u00eau xe Ferrari khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n c\u00f9ng Man City</span><br>\r\nH\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Mendy m\u1eebng ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng Les Bleus b\u1eb1ng Ferrari F2X m\u00e0u v\u00e0ng ch\u00f3e.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/vua-co-thay-moi-bellerin-da-len-tieng-che-bai-wenger-172-192519.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/9/vua-co-thay-moi-bellerin-da-len-tieng-che-bai-wenger.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/vua-co-thay-moi-bellerin-da-len-tieng-che-bai-wenger-172-192519.html\">V\u1eeba c\u00f3 th\u1ea7y m\u1edbi, Bellerin \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ch\u00ea bai Wenger</span><br>\r\n&ldquo;Arsenal l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n&rdquo; &ndash; h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Hector Bellerin ch\u00ea bai Wenger, sau kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1eabn d\u1eaft b\u1edfi Emery.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4959","checkdouble":"192535"},{"date":"11:21 02/08","title":"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 02/08","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/2/chuyen-nhuong-mu-hot-nhat-ngay-0208.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 \u0111ang ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 02/08.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mina l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a M.U \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 0208 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 0208 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/27/Chuyen-nhuong-MU-2018-hot-nhat-ngay-0208-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mina nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a M.U \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMU mua Yerry Mina l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a HLV Jose Mourinho, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh &ldquo;bom t\u1ea5n&rdquo; cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tu-bo-maguire-va-alderweireld-mu-muon-mua-mina-cua-barca-172-192523.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/11/tu-bo-maguire-va-alderweireld-mu-muon-mua-mina-cua-barca.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tu-bo-maguire-va-alderweireld-mu-muon-mua-mina-cua-barca-172-192523.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! Bom t\u1ea5n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a MU \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018</span><br>\r\nMU mua Yerry Mina l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a HLV Jose Mourinho, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh &ldquo;bom t\u1ea5n&rdquo; cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Mourinho mu\u1ed1n M.U chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i c\u1ee7a Real</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha, HLV Mourinho \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng M.U s\u1ebd chi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Toni Kroos v\u00e0 Gareth Bale c\u1ee7a Real Madrid trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ea1i gia Italia ch\u01b0a bu\u00f4ng tha Matteo Darmian</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Napoli mu\u1ed1n mua Matteo Darmian c\u1ee7a M.U. Theo t\u1edd Daily Mail, d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia v\u1eabn \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb m\u1edbi gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Sao Real t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i MU v\u00ec Mourinho</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng Mateo Kovacic quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gia nh\u1eadp M.U v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i do Mourinho x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>M.U kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng chi 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Harry Maguire</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Maguire\" title=\"Maguire\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/hlv-leicester-noi-gi-truoc-tin-don-mu-chieu-mo-maguire.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>M.U kh\u00f4ng chi 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Maguire</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">ESPN kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng chi 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua trung v\u1ec7 Harry Maguire c\u1ee7a Leicester, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1ed1i \u0111a 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Barca b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao kh\u1ee7ng MU</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Paul Pogba c\u1ee7a M.U, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u00e2y! C\u00e1i t\u00ean s\u1ebd d\u1eabn d\u1eaft MU n\u1ebfu Mourinho ra \u0111i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Zidane\" title=\"Zidane\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/ngay-hom-nay-18.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Zidane c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Mourinho d\u1eabn d\u1eaft M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Zidane d\u1eabn d\u1eaft MU thay Mourinho, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 chia tay s\u00e2n Old Trafford.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Yerry Mina n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c MU quan t\u00e2m?</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Yerry Mina ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1994 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Barca hay ra \u0111i \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Everton \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Marcos Rojo</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Goal, Everton \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Maros Rojo c\u1ee7a MU v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd d\u00f9ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n thu v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Mina c\u1ee7a Barca.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4958","checkdouble":"192540"},{"date":"08:41 02/08","title":"Olympic Iraq r\u00fat lui, m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 18 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/1/18/olympic-iraq-rut-lui-mon-bong-da-nam-asiad-18-co-the-phai-boc-tham-lai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, \u1ee6y ban Olympic Iraq \u0111\u00e3 r\u00fat \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam kh\u1ecfi ASIAD 18 sau khi \u0111\u1ed9i U16 c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y b\u1ecb t\u1ed1 c\u00e1o gian l\u1eadn tu\u1ed5i.</h2><h2>Olympic Iraq r\u00fat lui kh\u1ecfi ASIAD 2018</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n n\u00e0y l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean an ninh t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n bay Baghdad (Iraq) \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft 9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n U16 Iraq do s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u1ed9 chi\u1ebfu gi\u1ea3 khi \u0111ang l\u00e0m th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c xu\u1ea5t c\u1ea3nh sang Jordan h\u00f4m 30/7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng tin tr\u00ean, IFA \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf cu\u1ed9c \u0111i\u1ec1u tra v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 gian l\u1eadn tu\u1ed5i t\u00e1c \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i U16. Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ban \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00e0 do \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n U16 Iraq \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3 h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, IFA \u0111\u00e3 sa th\u1ea3i HLV Ali Hadi v\u00e0 \u00ea-k\u00edp tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd li\u00ean quan t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y. Ngo\u00e0i ra, 9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a U16 Iraq b\u1ecb b\u1eaft \u1edf s\u00e2n bay c\u0169ng s\u1ebd b\u1ecb c\u1ea5m kho\u00e1c \u00e1o c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia v\u0129nh vi\u1ec5n.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Olympic Iraq r\u00fat lui kh\u1ecfi ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Olympic Iraq r\u00fat lui kh\u1ecfi ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/10/Olympic-Iraq-rut-lui-khoi-ASIAD-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>S\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 gian l\u1eadn tu\u1ed5i khi\u1ebfn Olympic Iraq r\u00fat lui kh\u1ecfi ASIAD 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 \u0111\u00e1ng h\u1ed5 th\u1eb9n n\u00e0y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Iraq quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u00fat \u0111\u1ed9i Olympic kh\u1ecfi ASIAD 2018. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft IFA s\u1ebd t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi d\u1eebng m\u1ecdi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n tr\u1ebb \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e1ng 9 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tra nh\u1eefng v\u1ee5 vi\u1ec7c gian l\u1eadn c\u00f3 li\u00ean quan.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng nh\u1eadn ra\u00a0tr\u00ean trang\u00a0Wikipedia\u00a0c\u1ee7a ASIAD 2018, tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Iraq \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb x\u00f3a t\u00ean kh\u1ecfi b\u1ea3ng C. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, trang\u00a0Soccer Iraq\u00a0c\u00f2n \u0111\u0103ng d\u00f2ng tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i \u201cIraq \u0111\u00e3 r\u00fat kh\u1ecfi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Asian Games 2018 do nh\u1eefng lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 gian l\u1eadn tu\u1ed5i t\u00e1c\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c Olympic Iraq kh\u00f4ng tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD khi\u1ebfn b\u1ea3ng C m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 3 \u0111\u1ed9i \u00a0Trung Qu\u1ed1c, Syria v\u00e0 Timor Leste. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7t ra nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c trong vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 m\u1ea5t c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u, b\u1edfi hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng 3 \u0111\u1ed9i, hai b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u 5 \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 ba b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u 4 \u0111\u1ed9i. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y bu\u1ed9c ban t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ph\u1ea3i thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i c\u00e1ch ch\u1ecdn 4 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch th\u1ee9 ba t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i. V\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh to\u00e1n \u0111\u1ebfn.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-thu-tai-asiad-2018-gui-loi-canh-bao-toi-olympic-viet-nam-168-192493.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/doi-thu-tai-asiad-2018-gui-loi-canh-bao-toi-olympic-viet-nam.jpeg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-thu-tai-asiad-2018-gui-loi-canh-bao-toi-olympic-viet-nam-168-192493.html\">\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\n\u0110T Olympic Pakistan m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng trong b\u1ea3ng D m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam khi c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1ea5n...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-nhan-them-bat-loi-truoc-them-asiad-2018-168-192501.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/29/dt-olympic-viet-nam-nhan-them-bat-loi-truoc-them-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-nhan-them-bat-loi-truoc-them-asiad-2018-168-192501.html\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u1eadn th\u00eam b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nTheo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1eadn, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4957","checkdouble":"192516"}]}